---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ToggleDemo from '../components/ToggleDemo.jsx';
import FadeIn from '../components/FadeIn.jsx';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Unslop | The Human Web"
  description="A quiet filter for X, LinkedIn, and Reddit. Keep human signal. Hide algorithmic slop."
>
  <main class="scroll-deck">
    <section class="slide text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <FadeIn client:visible>
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight text-ink sm:text-7xl">
            The internet was built for connection.
          </h1>
        </FadeIn>
        <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.08}>
          <p class="mt-6 text-2xl italic text-ink/80 sm:text-3xl">
            Somewhere along the way, we became the product.
          </p>
        </FadeIn>
        <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.14}>
          <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl font-mono text-sm tracking-[0.02em] text-graphite sm:text-base">
            Unslop is a quiet filter for the noise. Available now for LinkedIn. Support for X and Reddit is coming
            soon.
          </p>
        </FadeIn>
        <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.22}>
          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
            <a
              href="https://chromewebstore.google.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-ink bg-ink px-6 py-3 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-paper transition hover:bg-paper hover:text-ink"
            >
              Add to Chrome - It's Free
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://buymeacoffee.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border border-ink px-6 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-ink transition hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper"
            >
              Fuel the mission ☕
            </a>
          </div>
        </FadeIn>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="slide">
      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl">
        <div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-8 left-0 right-0 hidden select-none font-mono text-xs leading-6 text-ink/[0.06] sm:block">
          <p>zx01 // ctr ↑ // bait // 0034 // mine attention // loop // loop // loop //</p>
          <p>engagement++ // outrage // novelty // ad_slot // optimize_time_on_platform //</p>
          <p>predictive_feed // harvest_focus // rage_cycle // monetization // retention //</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
          <FadeIn client:visible>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">Your attention is being mined.</h2>
          </FadeIn>
          <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.1}>
            <p class="mt-8 font-mono text-base leading-relaxed text-graphite sm:text-lg">
              Big Tech is engineered to spike your cortisol. They sell your focus to advertisers and bury real human
              connection under a mountain of algorithmic slop. They want you addicted. They want you doom-scrolling.
              I built Unslop to give you the web back.
            </p>
          </FadeIn>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="slide">
      <div class="w-full max-w-4xl text-center">
        <FadeIn client:visible>
          <h2 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-semibold sm:text-5xl">Experience the silence.</h2>
        </FadeIn>
        <ToggleDemo client:visible />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="slide">
      <div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl grid-cols-1 gap-14 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-20">
        <FadeIn client:visible>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold sm:text-5xl">The Unit Economics.</h2>
            <p class="mt-8 font-mono text-base leading-relaxed text-graphite">
              Most apps hide their costs to sell you &quot;unlimited&quot; plans. I can&apos;t do that because I
              don&apos;t sell your data.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
              It costs me exactly $0.001 in computing power to filter one single post.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-base leading-relaxed text-graphite">
              But sustainability isn&apos;t just about the server bill. It&apos;s about development time. Your
              subscription funds the hours needed to maintain detection accuracy as spam evolves, adapt the extension
              when sites change their code, and build support for X (Twitter) and Reddit.
            </p>
          </div>
        </FadeIn>
        <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.1}>
          <div class="border border-ink/25 bg-[#efede6] p-6 sm:p-8">
            <p class="font-mono text-sm leading-8 text-ink">
              &gt; Item_Cost: $0.001<br />
              &gt; Items_Scanned: 2,500<br />
              &gt; Raw_API_Cost: $2.50<br />
              &gt; Stripe_Fees: $0.45<br />
              &gt; Future_Dev: FUNDED<br />
              &gt; Net_Income: SUSTAINABLE<br />
              &gt; Status: INDEPENDENT
            </p>
          </div>
        </FadeIn>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="slide">
      <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col justify-between gap-14">
        <div>
          <FadeIn client:visible>
            <h2 class="text-center text-4xl font-semibold sm:text-5xl">Fair pricing. No math anxiety.</h2>
          </FadeIn>
          <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            <FadeIn client:visible>
              <article class="border border-ink/25 bg-paper p-7">
                <p class="font-serif text-2xl">The Tourist (Free)</p>
                <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-sm text-graphite">See how it feels to browse in peace.</p>
                <ul class="mt-8 space-y-2 font-mono text-sm text-ink">
                  <li>100 Scans / Month (Trial)</li>
                  <li>Works on LinkedIn</li>
                  <li>(X &amp; Reddit coming soon)</li>
                  <li>Runs out quickly (Good for testing)</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-3xl text-ink">$0 / forever</p>
                <a
                  href="https://chromewebstore.google.com"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noreferrer"
                  class="mt-8 inline-block border border-ink bg-ink px-5 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-paper transition hover:bg-paper hover:text-ink"
                >
                  Add to Chrome
                </a>
              </article>
            </FadeIn>
            <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.08}>
              <article class="border border-ink/25 bg-paper p-7">
                <p class="font-serif text-2xl">The Local (Paid)</p>
                <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-sm text-graphite">Reclaim your feed. Support the build.</p>
                <ul class="mt-8 space-y-2 font-mono text-sm text-ink">
                  <li>2,500 Scans / Month</li>
                  <li>Directly funds X &amp; Reddit support</li>
                  <li>Priority Processing &amp; Accuracy Updates</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-3xl text-ink">$5 / month</p>
                <a
                  href="mailto:support@getunslop.com?subject=Unslop%20Pro%20Subscription"
                  class="mt-8 inline-block border border-ink px-5 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-ink transition hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper"
                >
                  Subscribe
                </a>
              </article>
            </FadeIn>
          </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="pb-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-graphite">Built by a human..</p>
          <p class="mt-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-graphite">
            <a href="https://x.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-4">Twitter</a>
            •
            <a href="mailto:support@getunslop.com" class="underline underline-offset-4">Email</a>
            •
            <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-4">Buy me a coffee</a>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-graphite">
            <a href="/privacy.html" class="underline underline-offset-4">Privacy</a>
            •
            <a href="/support.html" class="underline underline-offset-4">Support</a>
            •
            <a href="/terms.html" class="underline underline-offset-4">Terms</a>
          </p>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
